x\mapsto ax+b
x\mapsto x\phi(x^{-1})
 \begin{split} \frac{d^2}{dx^2} x\phi(x^{-1})& =\frac{d}{dx}(\phi(x^{-1})-x^{-1}\phi'(x^{-1})) \\ &=-x^{-2}\phi'(x^{-1})+x^{-2}\phi'(x^{-1} )+x^{-3}\phi''(x^{-1}) \\  & =x^{-3}\phi''(x^{-1})  \end{split} \tag1
x\mapsto x(ax^{-1}+b)=a+bx
